sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Users<br/>(Web / Mobile)
    participant IDP as Identity Provider<br/>(Cognito / Entra External ID)
    participant Edge as Edge Security<br/>(WAF / TLS / DDoS Protection)
    participant Gateway as API Gateway<br/>(Rate limiting / Auth validation)
    participant BFF as BFF Layer<br/>(Journey-level validation)
    participant Services as Microservices<br/>(Service-level validation)
    participant Data as Data Layer<br/>(Encrypted storage)
    participant Monitor as Monitoring & Security<br/>(CloudWatch / GuardDuty)

    User->>IDP: 1. Login Request
    activate IDP
    IDP->>IDP: Authenticate user
    IDP->>User: 2. JWT Token
    deactivate IDP
    
    User->>Edge: 3. API Request + JWT
    activate Edge
    Edge->>Edge: WAF inspection<br/>TLS termination<br/>DDoS check
    Edge->>Gateway: 4. Forward request
    deactivate Edge
    
    activate Gateway
    Gateway->>Gateway: Rate limiting check<br/>Basic auth validation
    Gateway->>BFF: 5. Route request
    deactivate Gateway
    
    activate BFF
    BFF->>BFF: JWT validation (Journey-level)<br/>User context creation<br/>Authorization check
    BFF->>Services: 6. Service call + Context
    deactivate BFF
    
    activate Services
    Services->>Services: JWT validation (Service-level)<br/>RBAC + ABAC enforcement<br/>Business logic execution
    Services->>Data: 7. Data request
    deactivate Services
    
    activate Data
    Data->>Data: Access encrypted data<br/>(RDS / MongoDB / S3)<br/>TLS in transit
    Data->>Services: 8. Data response
    deactivate Data
    
    activate Services
    Services->>Monitor: 9. Log activity
    Services->>BFF: 10. Service response
    deactivate Services
    
    activate BFF
    BFF->>Gateway: 11. Response
    deactivate BFF
    
    activate Gateway
    Gateway->>Edge: 12. Response
    deactivate Gateway
    
    activate Edge
    Edge->>User: 13. Final response
    deactivate Edge
    
    Monitor->>Monitor: CloudWatch logs<br/>GuardDuty analysis<br/>Security auditing
    
    Note over User,Monitor: End-to-end encrypted communication with multiple validation layers